{"tid":381791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2支那客泰國遇劫遭劈頭毀容   嚴重失血","createTime":"2017-08-31T08:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T12:18:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":81,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d7be5c8589ce8a98f708c522db748e85ae489c","tid":381791,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170831/large/1504165449_3e69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170831%2Flarge%2F1504165449_3e69.jpg&h=fd694c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩名中國遊客在泰國旅行時，深夜遭持刀歹徒搶劫導致毀容。今日凌晨零時30分左右，劉姓中國男子（27歲）與夏姓女伴（28歲）步行返回酒店，途徑易三倉大學路附近，一名歹徒踩單車一路跟蹤他們，企圖搶走手袋，兩人拼命反抗，對方於是亮出生銹長刀，朝他們頭部亂斬。<br />\n<br />\n同一時間，一輛的士途徑現場，該歹徒迅速踩單車一無所獲下落荒而逃。的士司機下車準備救助劉男和夏女，但由於二人失血過多，司機報警。警方到場後將中國遊客送院治理，其中劉男前額被斬傷，夏女右耳則有一大道傷口，兩人嚴重失血。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，兇器為一把23寸長的刀，刀身有銹迹，傷者情況已見好轉，目前仍在深切治療部留醫。<br />\n<br />\n泰國網  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170831/large/1504165450_8ca1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170831%2Flarge%2F1504165450_8ca1.jpg&h=0c1a6703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170831/large/1504165451_509d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170831%2Flarge%2F1504165451_509d.jpg&h=9c77d006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170831/large/1504165452_af0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170831%2Flarge%2F1504165452_af0f.jpg&h=b3565547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170831/large/1504165453_2052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu